    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      269.38,
      108.09,
      332.15,
      121.37
    ],
    "text": "Judgement",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      143.86,
      143.3,
      157.14
    ],
    "text": "Introduction",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      183.36,
      526.33,
      196.64
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner, in this Application, seeks to obtain a Writ of Certiorari on the speculation that",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      210.2,
      525.98,
      224.42
    ],
    "text": "the 1st Respondent, who is the Divisional Secretary, may have issued a permit under the Land",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      237.7,
      526.1,
      251.92
    ],
    "text": "Development Ordinance to the 2nd Respondent, whom the Petitioner alleges came by force to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      266.14,
      525.9,
      279.42
    ],
    "text": "occupy a portion of the parcel of land that the Petitioner claims to have been in occupation of",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      293.91,
      129.8,
      307.19
    ],
    "text": "since 1960.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      333.41,
      526.02,
      346.69
    ],
    "text": "After initially supporting this application and obtaining the issuance of notice, the Respondents",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      361.16,
      526.36,
      374.44
    ],
    "text": "filed their objections and, together with the Objections, marked and annexed certain documents",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      388.68,
      306.38,
      401.96
    ],
    "text": "and moved for the dismissal of this Application.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      428.18,
      391.42,
      441.46
    ],
    "text": "This was argued before me on 25.02.2026; hence, this judgement.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      463.96,
      201.08,
      477.24
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner\u2019s position",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      499.46,
      525.91,
      512.74
    ],
    "text": "The Petitioner claims that she is the owner of the land in suit, and she further claims that she",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      526.96,
      526.4,
      540.24
    ],
    "text": "and her late husband had been in possession of the said land in extent of 1.2144 Hectare",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      554.73,
      298.13,
      568.01
    ],
    "text": "belonging to the Sri Lanka Sugar Corporation.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      590.24,
      526.47,
      603.52
    ],
    "text": "It is also her position that though the said land was initially vested in the Sugar Corporation,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      617.98,
      526.38,
      631.26
    ],
    "text": "since certain parcels of land were not arable for sugar cane cultivation, the Sugar Corporation",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      645.51,
      526.12,
      658.79
    ],
    "text": "did not utilise such parcels of the land, and the parcel of land that has been occupied by the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      673.01,
      526.12,
      686.29
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner from 1960 is one such land. Therefore, with the permission of the Sugar Corporation,",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 2,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      700.76,
      489.2,
      714.04
    ],
    "text": "the Petitioner and her husband had developed the land by having a coconut plantation.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      777.78,
      303.63,
      806.07
    ],
    "text": "4",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      72.59,
      526.47,
      85.87
    ],
    "text": "It is also the Petitioner\u2019s position that at one point of time during the 1990s, the Pradeshiya",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      100.09,
      526.47,
      113.37
    ],
    "text": "Sabha of the area had encroached upon the land, and thereafter, the Petitioner had instituted a",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      127.86,
      526.41,
      141.14
    ],
    "text": "vindicatory action against the same and obtained damages in the sum of Rs. 20,000/- (Twenty",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      155.36,
      526.2,
      168.64
    ],
    "text": "Thousand Rupees) from the District Court. Thereafter, though the Pradeshiya Sabha had",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      183.11,
      525.96,
      196.39
    ],
    "text": "appealed to this Court, the said appeal had been dismissed; therefore, the Petitioner claims that",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      210.64,
      231.35,
      223.92
    ],
    "text": "her rights have been established.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      245.2,
      526.41,
      259.42
    ],
    "text": "In the meantime, the 2nd Respondent, acting in collusion with the 1st Respondent, has carved",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      273.88,
      526.26,
      287.16
    ],
    "text": "out a certain portion of the land occupied and possessed by the Petitioner, and made attempts",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      300.47,
      526.47,
      314.69
    ],
    "text": "to erect a building. The Petitioner explains that there may have been permit issued by the 1st",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      328.22,
      532.22,
      342.44
    ],
    "text": "Respondent in respect of the said parcel of land now forcibly occupied by the 2nd Respondent.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      8.0,
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      364.66,
      525.94,
      377.94
    ],
    "text": "In addition to that, the Sugar Corporation has given its consent to issue a permit only to the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      392.18,
      526.42,
      405.46
    ],
    "text": "Petitioner since the Petitioner along with her husband has developed the land from 1960, having",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      419.93,
      517.72,
      433.21
    ],
    "text": "occupied the same; the said letter has been addressed to the Divisional Secretary of the area.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      455.43,
      410.67,
      468.71
    ],
    "text": "Therefore, the Petitioner has moved for inter alia the following relief;",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-ItalicMT",
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 3,
    "bbox": [
