    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      218.64,
      525.91,
      231.92
    ],
    "text": "As such, unless the authorities who are entrusted with the subject of land take a decision to",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      246.14,
      526.41,
      259.42
    ],
    "text": "allocate or alienate such land under the relevant laws, namely the State Lands Ordinance or the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
