  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      273.88,
      525.9,
      287.16
    ],
    "text": "Land Development Ordinance, the Sugar Corporation cannot permit anybody to possess the",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      301.41,
      526.4,
      314.69
    ],
    "text": "same. Therefore, the Petitioner has not shown any right accrued to her under statutory or",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      329.16,
      297.38,
      342.44
    ],
    "text": "common law to obtain the relief as prayed for.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      364.66,
      457.7,
      377.94
    ],
    "text": "Thus, it is my view that the Petitioner\u2019s relief is baseless and cannot be granted.",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
