    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      400.18,
      246.35,
      413.46
    ],
    "text": "Vindicatory action (in personam)",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldItal",
      "TimesNewRomanPS-BoldMT"
    ],
    "sizes": [
      12.0
    ]
  },
  {
    "page_number": 7,
    "bbox": [
      72.03,
      435.93,
      526.12,
      449.21
    ],
    "text": "In addition to that, I must also hold that though the Petitioner claims that there had been a case",
    "fonts": [
      "TimesNewRomanPSMT"
